snippet.title: MNEMOPHOBIA: Deadline - Teaser Trailer (FNaF Fangame)
snippet.description:
Mnemophobia: Deadline is a "point and click" style "Mascot Horror" that utilizes its developer's memories and greatest traumas to create the most frightening and horrible experiences a human could ever have.
